WEBVTT

00:00.772 --> 00:03.295
In New York City's war on crime,

00:03.295 --> 00:06.417
the worst criminal offenders
are pursued by the detectives

00:06.417 --> 00:08.302
of the Major Case Squad.

00:08.302 --> 00:10.025
These are their stories.

00:14.029 --> 00:15.372
It's our house.

00:15.372 --> 00:16.950
You gotta be invited.

00:17.267 --> 00:19.605
You're not. Good-bye.

00:19.887 --> 00:21.719
You need to back off, Charlie.

00:21.719 --> 00:23.909
What are you? Deaf and dumb?

00:23.909 --> 00:25.644
Door, use it.

00:25.644 --> 00:28.430
You need to stop now.

00:32.259 --> 00:35.559
Charlie, you're assaulting a cop.
How dumb is that?

00:38.729 --> 00:40.441
MCS, unit 25!

00:40.441 --> 00:43.624
Signal 10-13 inside at engine 29!

00:43.624 --> 00:46.086
- Officer assaulted!
- Back off!

00:46.086 --> 00:47.722
- All right, all right, all right.
- Back off.

00:47.722 --> 00:49.190
All right, what now?

00:49.420 --> 00:51.067
Charlie, come on, guy.

00:51.067 --> 00:53.561
It's cool. Just let it ride.
It's cool.

00:55.473 --> 00:58.166
Well, you got about 20 seconds.

00:59.265 --> 01:00.523
Screw you.

01:00.523 --> 01:02.988
I don't know about you,
but I don't go that way.

01:04.443 --> 01:05.691
Son of a bitch!

01:05.691 --> 01:08.598
- Get off him!
- Charlie!

01:10.413 --> 01:11.616
Stay out!

01:16.120 --> 01:18.058
- Come on, Charlie!
- Get off!

01:19.473 --> 01:22.834
MCS, unit 25, signal 10-13.

01:22.834 --> 01:24.419
